Good news from Abashi about the amount of (or lack thereof) experience in Kunark zones...<BR><BR>

Abashi said....</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT FACE="VERDANA" SIZE="-2"><B>posted 05-19-2000 03:50 PM</B></FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT FACE="Verdana" COLOR="#00478E" SIZE="-2">
Hello all,<BR><BR>

Based upon some of the posts here, we've reviewed the experience-point (XP) rewards in
the Kunark dungeons and some of the outdoor areas and found them to be deficient.
Dungeons on Kunark were in general supposed to be giving more experience than
equivalent level dungeons on the other three continents, where in-fact they were giving
slightly less.<BR><BR>

Over the next couple of days, we'll be updating the experience rewards for many of the
Kunark zones, making them more profitable in terms of experience, in light of the
increased difficulty and danger associated with them.<BR><BR>

We wish to extend thanks to the players who brought this issue to our attention.<BR><BR>

-Gordon</FONT><BR><BR>

<B><I>MadWand</I></B><BR><BR></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>	
